{"tid":603066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毆斃67歲翁　70歲疑兇落網","createTime":"2018-03-23T12:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T13:14:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40cb3feb3b6d7332ca62b33f229247eca8c7c050","tid":603066,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180323/20340564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F20340564&d=UMigsLiDAYQDA6SGr28idoM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=166a4c0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F20340564&h=f2e9ed19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180323/20340564</a><br />\n<br />\n毆斃67歲翁　70歲疑兇落網<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】警方偵破前日沙田瀝源邨「拳頭交」命案，事發29小時後昨晚在大埔太和邨拘捕70歲疑兇，並押返其大埔寓所搜證。消息稱，警方根據死者手機攝下的疑兇照片，再配合現場天眼片段鎖定疑兇身份，發現他於案發後曾乘港鐵返回大埔寓所，至昨晚採取拘捕行動。<br />\n<br />\n被捕70歲疑犯居大埔瑞安街一個唐樓單位，警方發現他被捕時衣物與犯案時不同，懷疑他曾回家更衣。至於案中遇害男子姓吳（67歲），人稱坤哥，警方將剖屍確定死因。<br />\n事發於前日下3時許，吳游水後行經瀝源邨華豐樓地下停車場，與一男子碰撞爭執口角，其間疑拿手機拍攝對方容貌，懷疑有人盛怒下拳頭施襲，吳雖還手但頭鼻中拳當場流血倒地昏迷，送院證實死亡，疑兇則逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方根據死者手機攝下的疑兇照片，再核對現場天眼確認疑兇身份，其後警方追查發現疑兇曾乘港鐵到大埔，至昨晚8時警方在太和邨發現疑兇，即表露身份將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姜偉康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180323/large/23la7p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F23la7p10.jpg&h=46239261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n70歲疑兇由探員押返大埔寓所調查。"},{"pid":"c844bef0203568e5e6ddfdac0ac25efb8854ea1c","tid":603066,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"70 歲先黎衰殺人"},{"pid":"abb3c6b02102b30047bfada09dc177d9b2960479","tid":603066,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c844bef0203568e5e6ddfdac0ac25efb8854ea1c","tid":603066,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"70 歲先黎衰殺人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"成本相對低"},{"pid":"104ad4c0487c4949f5a3ac5fc92043dbeef4ea5e","tid":603066,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c15a43851872febf4a82e6963cf735c05cf68596","tid":603066,"uid":77951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"成世人係未試過坐監 入去體驗下姐"},{"pid":"7a0ac47b0d11d2738163b92e6169463c39d49da3","tid":603066,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"案中遇害男子姓吳，人稱坤哥<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁邪嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8118ecf0537933fd41a769e76d0dafd8812ca18","tid":603066,"uid":133992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a0ac47b0d11d2738163b92e6169463c39d49da3","tid":603066,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"案中遇害男子姓吳，人稱坤哥<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁邪嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"睇黎下一個就到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0387ee5946eecd6cf340cabade659cb53da482","tid":603066,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"唔游水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}